PET FRIENDLY

Available Now!

Discover this enchanting three-level townhome nestled in a conveniently located community just minutes away from I-95, VRE, and shopping and dining destinations! This charming all-brick, three-bedroom haven is accompanied by hardwood floors that gracefully guide you through its inviting spaces. The kitchen showcases upgraded cabinets, exquisite countertops, and stainless steel appliances.

As you make your way downstairs, a finished basement welcomes you with brand new carpeting, creating a cozy retreat. Venture outside to find a delightful concrete patio that opens up to a fenced yard, providing a perfect blend of indoor and outdoor living. This meticulously crafted home is not just a residence; it's a sanctuary of comfort and style, where every detail has been carefully considered to enhance your living experience.

*Washer and Dryer Units Convey AS-IS

*Video Coming Soon

CREDIT: Good Credit Required
PETS: Yes, case-by-case
PET FEE: $450/pet non-refundable fee
UTILITIES: Tenant Pays All
APPLICATION FEE: $60 per applicant
SECURITY DEPOSIT: Minimum One month's rent (Please note that in certain cases, a double deposit may be required)
RESIDENT BENEFIT PACKAGE: $25/month
LEASING FEE: $125 One time due with Move-in Funds.

*APPLY TODAY TO GET PRE-APPROVED.*
Our Applications are valid for 90 days and can be applied to any of our properties you qualify for.

Listed and Professionally Managed By: 
MacDoc Property Management
